# install-roo-modes — Environment Configuration
# Copy this file to env.config and edit the values.
# This file is read by the agent (not by a script) to construct glab API calls.

# Full URL of the source repository (GitLab) containing mode definitions.
# The skill parses host and project path from this URL automatically.
